Kth Smallest

Link : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/kth-smallest-element5635/1

Implementation:

class Solution {
    public int kthSmallest(int[] arr, int k) {
        Arrays.sort(arr);
        int res=0;
        for(int i=0;i<arr.length;i++){
            if(i==k-1){
                res= arr[i];
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}
